    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793260/extras/3de731d56058040f7696a656e883157c.poster.avif?t=1754054896\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793260/extras/3de731d56058040f7696a656e883157c.webm?t=1754054896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>在《Delivery INC》中，你将经营一家送货公司，接上乘客，装上包裹食物，然后尽快把他们送到目的地。你的目标是接载乘客、包裹和食物，然后在顾客的耐心耗尽之前把它们交付。你需要同时处理多个送货任务，因此需要发挥你的快速决策与逻辑能力。由哪个司机来接下一单？他们是否应该在送货途中提取或运送另一批货物？制定出最好的规划和路线，不要让你的客户等待太久。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793260/extras/deafe9f43fe122076e7736f90eaf0d95.poster.avif?t=1754054896\" width=616 height=599 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793260/extras/deafe9f43fe122076e7736f90eaf0d95.webm?t=1754054896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>你的送货员有时候会面临艰难的挑战，迫使他们向你寻求有用的建议。做出明智的选择，避免灾难，扭转局面。抓住机会，探索多种可能性，并期待意料之外的随机元素，随时保持新鲜感。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793260/extras/0c516a64109e72d75a79b804a1dc9c39.poster.avif?t=1754054896\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793260/extras/0c516a64109e72d75a79b804a1dc9c39.webm?t=1754054896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>在世界上的任何一座城市开始你的业务。在真实的道路上考验你的技巧。每座城市都是采用真实世界的地图数据创建的。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793260/extras/f3df0a758e9f3af3759e561432b7ca8f.poster.avif?t=1754054896\" width=616 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793260/extras/f3df0a758e9f3af3759e561432b7ca8f.webm?t=1754054896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>你的车队和司机是成功经营一家送货公司的关键。每位司机都有独特的性格特征，会对他们的表现产生积极或消极的影响。每辆车都有各自的优势和劣势。组建一支最适合你公司和游戏风格的团队。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793260/extras/0d622622917a0225e82e2151a068ea02.poster.avif?t=1754054896\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1793260/extras/0d622622917a0225e82e2151a068ea02.webm?t=1754054896\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br>客户评价对公司的声誉会有很大影响，所以你必须确保每位客户都有最好的体验。较高的评分会增加客户数量和利润。较低的评分会让你的公司举步维艰。",
